org.activebpel.rt.xml.schema.sampledata
Class AeSampleDataVisitor

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.xml.schema.sampledata.AeSampleDataVisitor
All Implemented Interfaces:
IAeSampleDataVisitor
public class AeSampleDataVisitor
extends java.lang.Object
implements IAeSampleDataVisitor

A visitor class for generating XML sample data for a given Schema Element (of simpleType or complexType) as represented by an AeStructure object.

getRepeatCount

private int getRepeatCount(AeStructure aStructure)
Gets the preferred number of times to repeat instances of the given structure. Note that the results are guarenteed to be within the range of the structures specified minOccurs and maxOccurs range.

Parameters:
aStructure -
Returns:
int

getRepeatCount

private int getRepeatCount(javax.xml.namespace.QName aElementName,
                           AeStructure aStructure)
Gets the preferred number of times to repeat instances of the given structure. Note that the results are guarenteed to be within the range of the structures specified minOccurs and maxOccurs range. If the structure being potentially repeated is an element, then the element qname is passed, otherwise null is passed.

Parameters:
aStructure -
Returns:
int
